---
// Static recreation of euterria.org's semantic-reranker figure: one
// shortlist of candidates, first ordered by keyword score, then reordered
// by a reranking model reading for meaning. The keyword winner sinks; the
// person the query never named by phrase rises to the top. Colours encode
// entity type, to show the reranker sorting across different kinds of thing.
---
<figure class="rrk">
  <div class="rrk-card">
    <div class="rrk-grid">
      <div class="rrk-col">
        <p class="rrk-head">Keyword shortlist</p>
        <ol class="rrk-list">
          <li class="rrk-item"><span class="rrk-rank">1</span><span class="rrk-dot" style="background:#2E8FA3"></span><span class="rrk-label">Heat &amp; Health Report</span></li>
          <li class="rrk-item"><span class="rrk-rank">2</span><span class="rrk-dot" style="background:#2E8FA3"></span><span class="rrk-label">Citywide Tree Census</span></li>
          <li class="rrk-item"><span class="rrk-rank">3</span><span class="rrk-dot" style="background:#6D5BD0"></span><span class="rrk-label">Oakland Shade Plan</span></li>
          <li class="rrk-item"><span class="rrk-rank">4</span><span class="rrk-dot" style="background:#C77A2B"></span><span class="rrk-label">Dr. Maya Okonkwo</span></li>
          <li class="rrk-item"><span class="rrk-rank">5</span><span class="rrk-dot" style="background:#1F6E3C"></span><span class="rrk-label">GreenLine Collaborative</span></li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="rrk-mid" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="rrk-mid-label">semantic reranker</span>
        <span class="rrk-mid-arrow"></span>
      </div>

      <div class="rrk-col">
        <p class="rrk-head">Reranked by meaning</p>
        <ol class="rrk-list">
          <li class="rrk-item rrk-item--top"><span class="rrk-rank">1</span><span class="rrk-dot" style="background:#C77A2B"></span><span class="rrk-label">Dr. Maya Okonkwo</span><span class="rrk-move rrk-move--up">▲&nbsp;3</span></li>
          <li class="rrk-item"><span class="rrk-rank">2</span><span class="rrk-dot" style="background:#6D5BD0"></span><span class="rrk-label">Oakland Shade Plan</span><span class="rrk-move rrk-move--up">▲&nbsp;1</span></li>
          <li class="rrk-item"><span class="rrk-rank">3</span><span class="rrk-dot" style="background:#1F6E3C"></span><span class="rrk-label">GreenLine Collaborative</span><span class="rrk-move rrk-move--up">▲&nbsp;2</span></li>
          <li class="rrk-item"><span class="rrk-rank">4</span><span class="rrk-dot" style="background:#2E8FA3"></span><span class="rrk-label">Heat &amp; Health Report</span><span class="rrk-move rrk-move--down">▼&nbsp;3</span></li>
          <li class="rrk-item"><span class="rrk-rank">5</span><span class="rrk-dot" style="background:#2E8FA3"></span><span class="rrk-label">Citywide Tree Census</span><span class="rrk-move rrk-move--down">▼&nbsp;3</span></li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rrk-legend">
      <span><i style="background:#C77A2B"></i>Person</span>
      <span><i style="background:#6D5BD0"></i>Program</span>
      <span><i style="background:#1F6E3C"></i>Organization</span>
      <span><i style="background:#2E8FA3"></i>Resource</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <figcaption>The same five candidates, ranked by keyword score, then reordered by a reranking model reading for meaning. The keyword winner sinks to fourth; the person the query never named by phrase rises to first.</figcaption>
</figure>
